Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In the year After Colony 175...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...the leader of the colonies\Nwas assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Five Gundams were sent\Nto Earth to take revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.60,0:01:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,However, since OZ's activities\Nin space...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...took the form of cooperation\Nrather than control...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...the colonies decided\Nto accept OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The year After Colony 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As OZ moves to take over\Nboth Earth and outer space...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...Gundams are labeled rebels\Nand are isolated from society.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,With no place to return...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Gundams and\Ntheir pilots...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...must fight for a reason to\Nexist in the changing world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and return, Zechs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not around to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...OZ will allow worthless\Nactions by worthless people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Treize...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can no longer be your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Howard, look at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You were piloting that\Ninteresting machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I picked it up, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would have guessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...that anyone other than those\Nkids could pilot the Tallgeese.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm one of the people who\Nwas involved in its design.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you made the Tallgeese?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sailing through this area...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I saw an intense battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I stuck around to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you bother\Nto save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become OZ's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs Merquise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ's very own hero has\Nbroken away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no harm in\Ntaking care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs Merquise is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The times are changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to see the new era\Nwhile I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fabulous piece\Nof machinery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder it's the prototype\Nfor the Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those vernier rockets\Nfor atmospheric clearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, they were\Noriginally manufactured...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...to get the Gundams\Nback into outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you can make it\Nto outer space?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Outer space?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about to undergo\Na drastic transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a growing need for\Nskilled people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ started cracking down...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...on the former United Earth\NSphere Alliance Space Force...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...stationed at La Grange Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ was steadily increasing its\Nstrength within the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Space Fortress Barge was\Nsymbolic of this strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But OZ didn't reveal its\Naggressive side...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...to the colony citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, it showed a completely\Ndifferent aspect of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ's Colonel Une replaced\Nthe former Alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...as the Commander\Nof the Space Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She formed relations with\Nrepresentatives of the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,With a sense of liberation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...from the militaristic\Npressure of the Alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...the colonies were welcoming\NOZ in its new establishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to attain peace\Nand to coexist...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...in the colonies and within\Nthe whole Earth Sphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...we must have your\Ncooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately though, some\Npeople within the colonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...are doubtful of OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They point out mistakes\Nthat were made in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I believe that\Nthe day will come...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...when these people will\Nunderstand OZ's efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We feel they'll change\Ntheir minds as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're trying hard to\Nconvince each of the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, we have\Nno means to counter violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what OZ is here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as OZ is present...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...I have no doubt that\Njustice will be served.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If Colonel Une says so,\Nthen there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Once peace spreads into space...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...even those who still\Nharbor doubts toward OZ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...will awaken to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Une!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the item in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel, please return to Barge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To Barge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders from His Excellency\NTreize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,His Excellency Treize...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll return to Barge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the HLV carrier that left\NEarth carrying a Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundams are evil and\Nwill harm the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd be valuable as\Nour evil scapegoats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring out the Tauruses!\NCapture it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Depends on his looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's ugly, let him live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If people could sympathize\Nwith him, then kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have anything\Ninterfere with...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...changing public opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him live if he's ugly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have confirmation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's an HLV from Singapore{\i0}\N{\i1}used to transport a Gundam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No energy detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle it flew\Nthis far without refueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It might be unmanned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless, orders are\Nto capture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll tow it along to\NColony C 102.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What an honor, being\Ngreeted by the latest model.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyone carelessly\Napproaching me will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taurus mobile dolls, attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That didn't work either!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero output.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My Deathscythe's bought it\Nand I don't have long myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, I'll die fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam, you're just lucky\Nthat I wasn't a mobile doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to copy\NHeero, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tag along, on my\Njourney into hell!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not my lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't even self-detonate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe...I am lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One of the Gundam{\i0}\N{\i1}mobile suits...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...known for their destruction{\i0}\N{\i1}and threat to peace...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...was shot down by{\i0}\N{\i1}OZ's Taurus unit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Gundam pilot has{\i0}\N{\i1}been arrested.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The background of this pilot{\i0}\N{\i1}has not been confirmed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But OZ has said that{\i0}\N{\i1}the arrest will assist them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...as they attempt to eradicate{\i0}\N{\i1}rebels and their organizations.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The colony governments have{\i0}\N{\i1}announced their cooperation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hopefully with the cooperation{\i0}\N{\i1}of OZ and the colonies...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...we will soon be able{\i0}\N{\i1}to return to total peace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the people of the colonies\Nso used to being controlled...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...that nobody can figure out\Nthe Gundams are the only ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I have no choice left\Nbut to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too far away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's near the colony\NHeero went to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll do something, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,After Colony 175.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No major incidents within\Nthe colonies?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The assassination of the leader\NHeero Yuy has been deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ's methods haven't\Nchanged one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}OZ has said that{\i0}\N{\i1}this will assist them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...as they attempt to{\i0}\N{\i1}eradicate rebels...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This wouldn't be the\Nright time for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All negative factors\Nmust be eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flight 0904, proceed to R28.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Proceed to R28...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Following the capture{\i0}\N{\i1}of the mad scientists...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...who were foes to the colonies{\i0}\N{\i1}and the people of Earth...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...one of the Gundams and{\i0}\N{\i1}its pilot have now been caught.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Colony C 102 authorities are{\i0}\N{\i1}calling OZ's actions a success.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They say they'll continue to{\i0}\N{\i1}promote cooperative efforts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray for OZ!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting the Gundam\Npilot to be just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I wounded your pride?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not compared to how\Nyour pride has suffered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The people's feelings toward the\Nexecution will unite the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected to use\Nthe Gundam pilots this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, they did me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise, Heero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are superhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They were about to use me and\Nmy Gundam for their plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm gonna die, then this\Nseems like the way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're seriously gonna\Nshoot me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your right hand's still okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where's your Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I left it on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd stick out, here in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'd get caught like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How will you get\Nus out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't thought up\Nan escape plan yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we don't make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as simple as silencing\Nthe two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always the quiet guys\Nwho're the flashiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Several small bombs have been{\i0}\N{\i1}set in the supplies block!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Increase security around\Nthe Gundam pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Surveillance here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Gundam pilot has escaped{\i0}\N{\i1}with an outsider's help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the Gundam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There were explosions{\i0}\N{\i1}in the area.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But no sign of intruders.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me the explosion points.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Explosions are centered around\Nthe supplies storage and gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The mobile suit gate and area\Nis untouched!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy will escape\Nfrom there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Send out the dolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't target settings be\Ndifficult within the colony?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The dolls aren't a\Ncheap system!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're annihilation machines!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Deploy them at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enemy attack in Colony C 102!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Backup troops, head{\i0}\N{\i1}there at once!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can show me\Nwhat you're made of!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sending Tauruses\Nto attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Une!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A Gundam is right by the base!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's going to a colony{\i0}\N{\i1}meeting in a new district.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This couldn't be all you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You people are strong enough\Nto control the colony citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're underhanded and\Nmuch stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Nichol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam Zero Five and the Leos\Nin pursuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...are in the firing range\Nof Barge's Beam Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, fire!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But we'd fire on our Leos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it before the Colonel leaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam Zero Five is within\Nfiring range!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fire!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrificing your own men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen the enemy\Nas foul as they are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When deceitful guys like you\Nare strong, I can fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, stop this futile battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let us greet a new age together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's do away with any{\i0}\N{\i1}desires to battle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...which were left over{\i0}\N{\i1}from the passing era.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such destructive desires{\i0}\N{\i1}aren't needed in the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taurus troops, we're moving{\i0}\N{\i1}in on the Gundam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please end this futile battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Une, please give us\Norders to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't do that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Peace should prevail{\i0}\N{\i1}in outer space.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, attack Zero Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait OZ;\NI'll come back to get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- We're going after Zero Five!{\i0}\N{\i1}- Sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:18:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Which Colonel am I\Nsupposed to follow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.18,0:19:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So those new models\Nare the mobile dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder their reaction\Ntime is quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they're locked onto\Na target, there's no escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how will we get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not thinking about escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Duo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We could use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are the mobile dolls\Nattacking the Leos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A Leo was scrambling\Nto get off the premises.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So the mobile dolls\Nset it as a target!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems another\Ntarget has been set.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an astro suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The astro suit has also\Nbeen set as a target!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel the auto command!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel it! Hurry!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I left my Gundam behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundams are worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. J and the other scientists\Nwho designed the Gundams...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...have all been caught by OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eliminate all obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going overboard,\Nto get one person into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.82,0:22:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Outer space is rejecting humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.56,0:22:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And perhaps the Earth is\Ntelling us we're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...by pulling us back down\Ntoward it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.75,0:23:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The five scientists start\Ndeveloping OZ's new suits...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...Mercurius and Vayeate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In an attempt to stop them...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...Heero sneaks on the Lunar\NBase to assassinate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's stopped in his tracks\Nby none other than Trowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, on Gundam Wing, Episode 20,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.60,0:23:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Lunar Base Infiltration".
